    `version_number` STRING COMMENT 'Semantic version number of the application release following major.minor.patch format (e.g., 3.2.1, 4.0.0-beta). This is the externally-known identifier for the release. | Column version_number (STRING) in distribution.app_version. Valid values are `^d+.d+.d+(.[w-]+)?$`',
    CONSTRAINT pk_app_version PRIMARY KEY(`app_version_id`)
