    `rollout_percentage` DECIMAL(18,2) COMMENT 'Percentage of the target audience to which the feature is rolled out (0.00 to 100.00). Enables gradual feature deployment and canary releases. | Column rollout_percentage (DECIMAL(5,2)) in distribution.feature_flag',
