    `accessibility_obligation_id` BIGINT COMMENT 'Foreign key linking to compliance.accessibility_obligation. Business justification: Linear channels have specific closed captioning, audio description, and accessibility compliance obligations under FCC CVAA rules. Each channel tracks its applicable obligations for compliance reporti | Column accessibility_obligation_id (BIGINT) in compliance.delivery_channel',
