    `allowed_countries` STRING COMMENT 'Comma-separated list of ISO 3166-1 alpha-3 country codes where content playback is permitted. | Column allowed_countries (STRING) in distribution.drm_policy',
    `analog_output_control` STRING COMMENT 'Policy governing analog video output (allowed, restricted with downscaling, or completely blocked). | Column analog_output_control (STRING) in distribution.drm_policy. Valid values are `allowed|restricted|blocked`',
    `analog_sunset_enabled` BOOLEAN COMMENT 'Flag indicating whether analog output is progressively restricted or disabled (analog sunset policy). | Column analog_sunset_enabled (BOOLEAN) in distribution.drm_policy',
