    `bandwidth_limit_gbps` DECIMAL(18,2) COMMENT 'The maximum bandwidth capacity provisioned for this CDN configuration in gigabits per second. Exceeding this limit may trigger throttling or overage charges. | Column bandwidth_limit_gbps (DECIMAL(10,2)) in distribution.cdn_configuration',
