    `geo_blocking_mode` STRING COMMENT 'Specifies whether the geo-blocking rules operate as an allow-list (whitelist) or deny-list (blacklist) of countries. | Column geo_blocking_mode (STRING) in distribution.cdn_configuration. Valid values are `allow_list|deny_list`',
