    `provisioned_date` DATE COMMENT 'Date when the signal route was initially provisioned and configured in the broadcast or streaming infrastructure. | Column provisioned_date (DATE) in distribution.signal_route',
    `qos_tier` STRING COMMENT 'Quality of Service tier assigned to this signal route, determining priority, bandwidth allocation, and service level guarantees. | Column qos_tier (STRING) in distribution.signal_route. Valid values are `premium|standard|basic`',
    `route_code` STRING COMMENT 'Standardized alphanumeric code uniquely identifying the signal route in operational systems and documentation. | Column route_code (STRING) in distribution.signal_route',
