    `route_type` STRING COMMENT 'Classification of the signal routing path based on delivery technology and infrastructure (linear broadcast, OTT streaming, hybrid, satellite uplink, terrestrial transmission, IP interconnect). | Column route_type (STRING) in distribution.signal_route. Valid values are `linear_broadcast|ott_streaming|hybrid|satellite_uplink|terrestrial|ip_interconnect`',
    `source_code` STRING COMMENT 'Medallion lineage tracking column for bronze->silver->gold tracing | Column source_id (STRING) in distribution.signal_route',
